\f4\fs33\fsmilli16800 \cf11 \cb5 \strokec11 For me the biggest change is around @Properties / @Property, defin\'ading OSGi prop\'ader\'adties in your code. You can now spec\'adi\'adfy a prop\'ader inter\'adface which gives you type-safe\'adty for free. To end this, there is no need any\'admore to \'91read\'92 the prop\'ader\'adties in the @Activate-method.\cb1 \
\cb5 Let me show you this in code:\cb1 \
